<Link id="l00596" /><CodeLine lineNumber="596"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// An instruction propagated through the simulated instruction pipeline.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00597" /><CodeLine lineNumber="597"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00598" /><CodeLine lineNumber="598"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// This class is used to monitor changes to the internal state of instructions</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00599" /><CodeLine lineNumber="599"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// that are sent to the various components of the simulated hardware pipeline.</span></CodeLine>
